Package Conditions

Interface Summary
IConvertable interface for all conditions that are convertable to Asbru-conditions
 

Class Summary
CombinedCondition condition to combine many conditions with logic operators
ComparisonCondition condition for comparisons
ConditionBase base class for any type of conditions
ContainsCondition<T> condition to model if a value or a field is contained in a list of values or fields
IteratorEndCondition condition for iterator at end
IteratorStartCondition condition for iterator at start
NotCondition models the negation of a condition
OccuranceCondition condition to check the occurance of an instance
RangeCondition condition to check if a value is between to other values
VariableKnownCondition condition to check if a variable is known
VariableUnknownCondition condition to check if a variable is unknown
 

Enum Summary
ComparisonMemberType defines the different types of comparison
DirectionType direction-type of occurance condition
InstanceTyp instance type for occurance condition
LogicOperatorType operators for logic operations in ComparisonCondition
MatchCode match-codes for comparisons of fields and values
StateType state types for the occurance condition
